title: Diagnologic for Radiology
description:
Diagnologic - Social Network in radiology
More than 45 000 radiologists are already members of Diagnologic.
Diagnologic is the first social network in radiology

Diagnologic is exclusively reserved to radiologists and healthcare professionals
With Diagnologic you can :
	- Improve your knowledge in radiology
	- Share interesting radiologic cases with worldwide radiologists
	- Discuss or get second opinions from top sub specialists
	- Follow any sub specialty in radiology to have the info you want
	- Stay informed of the latest radiologic news
	- Create your own case collection
	- Obtain urgent  feedback when you need them

You got access at our highly classified collection of more than 10 000 radiologic cases (CT, x-rays, MRI, radiography).

Everyday, many cases of radiology are posted and commented by lots of radiologists. Join our community !
